  <name>Myrient Viewer</name>
  <summary>Browse and download files from Myrient file archive</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Myrient Viewer is a desktop application for browsing the Myrient file archive,
      with a focus on retro gaming content. Features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Browse Myrient's file structure with an intuitive interface</li>
      <li>Queue multiple files for download</li>
      <li>Generate wget and curl scripts for batch downloads</li>
      <li>Region-based filtering for game ROMs</li>
      <li>Fast search across directories</li>
      <li>Export download queues in multiple formats</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
